videos.description: Florida's Egor Koulechov takes the foul as he drains a 3-pointer for the Gators.
videos.headline: Koulechov makes the 4-point play

videos.description: Deaundrae Ballard finger rolls in the layup and draws a foul on the drive for the Gators.
videos.headline: Ballard rolls in and-1

videos.description: Keith Stone gets a block to set up a fastbreak 3-pointer from Egor Koulechov for the Gators.
videos.headline: Florida block leads to fastbreak 3

videos.description: KeVaughn Allen doesn't slow down on this massive one-handed jam for Florida.
videos.headline: Allen throws down huge dunk for Gators

videos.description: Kevarrius Hayes takes advantage of some miscommunication on the switch and slams home the pass from Egor Koulechov.
videos.headline: Florida pick-and-roll leads to open dunk

videos.description: Wajid Aminu goes up strong and slams home over Florida's Mike Okauru.
videos.headline: North Florida's Aminu dunks over Okauru
